{"tid":839420,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳展鵬：我會懷疑想同我一齊嘅人係咪想借我上位","createTime":"2018-09-28T02:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T09:05:53.000Z","uid":158180,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d58d98dc14aceb45cef3045f567a0104474267cf","tid":839420,"uid":158180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:48:44.000Z","msg":"陳展鵬自從宣佈同單文柔結婚，唔少人會諗起胡定欣。煎Pang同胡定欣疑幻似真嘅關係，又真係幾得意嘅，如果只係螢幕情侶或緋聞，咁佢哋又唔使好似好唔like對方，同場會面阻阻兼又ig互相unfollow！講番入行24年嘅煎Pang，佢嘅緋聞女友有姚嘉雯、鍾嘉欣、黃智雯、胡定欣。不過，佢肯承認嘅只有姚嘉雯，仲要係分咗手先肯認。煎Pang以前做訪問時講過，佢話當時分手係因為自己為事業搏殺緊，拍劇時間長，拍拖連見面時間都冇，唔想耽誤女友嘅幸福，所以忍痛分手。佢最近嘅訪問又講，佢話娛樂圈多采多姿，會懷疑想同佢一齊嘅人係咪想借佢上位！咁其實當時佢同姚嘉雯分手，係唔想耽誤對方，定係覺得對方係想借佢上位？抑或係煎Pang想曲線暗示，所有同佢傳過緋聞嘅女星，都係想借佢上位，包括視后胡定欣？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180927/626783?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180927%2F626783%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=W6PjhoFvK8ROuJVkWtKXgG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b74943fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180927%2F626783%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=0cc3e468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180927/626783?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條友係咪On 9? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4993d8cf747cb670e1bcd678f6eac93ee1b873","tid":839420,"uid":35014,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcfddde3a28a94708243b9e675b268bbd